{"tid":100702,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[真人真事]我係先知嘅後人，你問我答","createTime":"2017-01-30T09:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T14:19:29.000Z","uid":74353,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"979fd9014a9050c7eeaae282b94a697449fcc4a6","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:05:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的，<br />\n細細個嘅時候老母已經講好多希臘神話比我聽，我仲奇怪緊點解佢咁撚熟嗰度嘅歷史。直到年初一佢話比我知，我係阿波羅先知嘅後人。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b928bbc26e836909967cad35f76d8a2a1a780fec","tid":100702,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:07:33.000Z","msg":"痴線佬"},{"pid":"32f00682ae59d14ca22d39d6ad311539dfb713c8","tid":100702,"uid":34300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:08:30.000Z","msg":"講下盤古開天係關係?"},{"pid":"c95fc67c083892957d35fb477bc2534e139d00d1","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:12:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講下盤古開天係關係?</blockquote><br />\n巴打，我係希臘嗰邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df116eeb6419fe3c165b6aa21eaa5dafb2c7462","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:13:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴線佬</blockquote><br />\n我覺得係得老母痴咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00451c567e1874446f43bfd12110397306061ed","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699a198dbc01a3ec24f3ab1fe43b50f769d7a4a0","tid":100702,"uid":29355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:25:10.000Z","msg":"Hello 你有無事"},{"pid":"9e80af60a624cc833ccda7c6ed092e595d3f5ef6","tid":100702,"uid":34300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:25:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講下盤古開天係關係?</blockquote><br />\n巴打，我係希臘嗰邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁點睇當年后羿溝左維納斯，之後維納斯偷左粒不死藥上左月亮??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f51aa0fb55f15f6cb73d8b58e488ec01732cea","tid":100702,"uid":56199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:26:33.000Z","msg":"邊個會上任"},{"pid":"29bf773c00d43c9841d8b1345b7455d93c348ee1","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:31:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講下盤古開天係關係?</blockquote><br />\n巴打，我係希臘嗰邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁點睇當年后羿溝左維納斯，之後維納斯偷左粒不死藥上左月亮??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n維納斯係嫁咗比火神赫菲斯托斯，后羿啲嘢我就唔撚知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce87ce89d0e781f7aec4bc1d1de48ada0dd81d0","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:32:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個會上任</blockquote><br />\nI got no idea <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4bbd6fe15d88079ea280568823a5ec0e3760b5","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:33:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Hello 你有無事</blockquote><br />\n多謝關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你想知啲咩"},{"pid":"cb1eadea159cdddbbdd22db2b8e01bc6e502aa13","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:35:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的，<br />\n細細個嘅時候老母已經講好多希臘神話比我聽，我仲奇怪緊點解佢咁撚熟嗰度嘅歷史。直到年初一佢話比我知，我係阿波羅先知嘅後人。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多巴絲都問我有無病，我具體少少講自己background 先。<br />\n<br />\n喺特洛伊戰爭時期左右面（你當4000至5000年前），有個女祭師叫 卡珊德拉 ，佢拒絕咗阿波羅嘅強姦，阿波羅懲罰佢所講嘅預言全部唔會有人信，最後佢比阿伽門儂(討伐特洛伊嘅 &lsquo;大英雄&rsquo; ) 俘虜咗返希臘，繼而比阿伽門儂老婆殺死。<br />\n而老母話比我知，真相係卡珊德拉返緊希臘中途，阿波羅今次真係強姦咗佢。真係好撚仆街，不過就係咁，呢一個先知/ 詛咒嘅血統流撚到今日。"},{"pid":"826e798b3c6b6d7f3c260817fe1cf8a9f8e96acc","tid":100702,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:37:52.000Z","msg":"宙司有冇嚟過香港搞大過邊個個肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知我有冇機會做神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525877c778130298df34c2f124fde8b5198ccb9a","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:43:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宙司有冇嚟過香港搞大過邊個個肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知我有冇機會做神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人唔會做到神，so far 得海格力斯 一個做到，但佢本身都係半神。<br />\n半神都會死，其實半神係勁啲嘅人啦你當係<br />\n<br />\n宙斯屌完女唔洗向人交待啦呀哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe88c1541f5f97ca265b20ad8268faedaa6f317a","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95430fd8d1e36bef14c48073c987716b35cf39fd","tid":100702,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:59:52.000Z","msg":"你大鑊啦 我老母話比我知唔好亂咁向其他人透露自己係先知嘅後人 如果唔係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931adce7cfafd6b180f42fec37668d23524ba4f3","tid":100702,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ba4830816a7e3b72927be9211273ee5bc70558","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:05:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你大鑊啦 我老母話比我知唔好亂咁向其他人透露自己係先知嘅後人 如果唔係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你老母咩料？"},{"pid":"ac543c30a793a5147f099c90d62c5a3100a419bf","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:06:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真話無人信"},{"pid":"d15a79a23dd966f84f68ad998b5ca785985b7950","tid":100702,"uid":71726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:08:50.000Z","msg":"神通常係邊到扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c3f5564362fd620424ccc43d0ad274de0ee7ef","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:12:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>神通常係邊到扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n神同神就 奧林匹斯山<br />\n<br />\n宙斯會屌人類，以前佢會變牛變鷹嚟溝女，而家唔知佢會咩玩法... <br />\n溝大陸妹會變iPhone 掛"},{"pid":"875f09194dd2171fbe4a4c6d654b34057f704601","tid":100702,"uid":960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/30/181309_c3c18a354ed6d31a83b774d50edecf24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F30%2F181309_c3c18a354ed6d31a83b774d50edecf24.jpg&h=d6b7833d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先知後人都要失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇預見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac15eb6d7b4cd2a4105421cee16c5ee102f122d","tid":100702,"uid":76152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:15:04.000Z","msg":"依加佢地仲會唔會落黎溝女"},{"pid":"c4086d6deb8df2e3144e17286a7442be5fadada0","tid":100702,"uid":649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:16:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/30/181309_c3c18a354ed6d31a83b774d50edecf24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F30%2F181309_c3c18a354ed6d31a83b774d50edecf24.jpg&h=d6b7833d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先知後人都要失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇預見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慘"},{"pid":"6885189ea03865c99f4024cf03a873c36f1cf46d","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:16:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/30/181309_c3c18a354ed6d31a83b774d50edecf24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F30%2F181309_c3c18a354ed6d31a83b774d50edecf24.jpg&h=d6b7833d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先知後人都要失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇預見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你，我都話最近老母先話我知我係後人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95432132232768fdd526becca70df37166875504","tid":100702,"uid":606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:19:00.000Z","msg":"咩係先知"},{"pid":"d535fa6e97d9897bdd5e36de033ede3d5258334d","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:20:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依加佢地仲會唔會落黎溝女</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n廿歲人一次神諭都未收過。<br />\n我諗有都唔出奇，但無先知知，知都無人寫<br />\n天神唔想留底掛"},{"pid":"70458fe952c7279a1025defe0c04bdeec309ba7a","tid":100702,"uid":55972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:21:08.000Z","msg":"點睇聖經，外星人，靈魂"},{"pid":"df13e6814944c93599c4ff20c2fc639c5ae30f1c","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:21:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩係先知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你當係寫手，天神要你寫佢想你寫底嘅嘢<br />\n我有無認真咗？"},{"pid":"2e148838c220e11755a179aac3866efb6a28f02f","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:23:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇聖經，外星人，靈魂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解會溝埋呢三樣嚟問？ <br />\n我咁睇，全部都係人類嘅想像力。"},{"pid":"40984c25ae3c64258ad0cb9278fcc9939bcb1445","tid":100702,"uid":35478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:24:46.000Z","msg":"同你買撈麵有無折?"},{"pid":"3ef2f6fe4854899913e0d65cb6d38002ca249790","tid":100702,"uid":960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:25:46.000Z","msg":"金莎喺咪真喺天神送俾我哋嘅禮物？"},{"pid":"e00d56dabf46108a98810d17c470ab651963afcb","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"今年老母同我講完，我心諗一句做乜鳩之後，就無理到，因為親戚都無再講呢樣嘢。啲奇怪嘢就嚟喇，年初二見到好撚多烏鴉(阿波羅聖物) ，又好唔知點解撚驚陽光，好怕會有空襲、有箭射落嚟咁 (阿波羅佢係神箭手) ，加埋咁勁煙霞仲驚，睇唔到上面咩樣。好在拜年都係親戚過嚟，無咩要出去... <br />\n<br />\n講明，我係驚多過信"},{"pid":"b2a974eeaf5e6226870a2f73f322d52bee4f6f84","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:26:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你買撈麵有無折?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜撚嘢問題嚟架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4f556ffe5661a053ba110b99c219bbdd6900af","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:28:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金莎喺咪真喺天神送俾我哋嘅禮物？</blockquote><br />\n五糧液先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3fa75cbc60232606dd464fbe82328810b10943b","tid":100702,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:30:22.000Z","msg":"過年青山放監?"},{"pid":"d3a0d0e7db8d153b1522dc24acb4fdadcb71867e","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:33:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過年青山放監?</blockquote><br />\n係咩？你有fd 出咗嚟？"},{"pid":"afc749d9835431e2b7542745eabd12979c4af787","tid":100702,"uid":960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:34:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>是咁的，<br />\n細細個嘅時候老母已經講好多希臘神話比我聽，我仲奇怪緊點解佢咁撚熟嗰度嘅歷史。直到年初一佢話比我知，我係阿波羅先知嘅後人。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多巴絲都問我有無病，我具體少少講自己background 先。<br />\n<br />\n喺特洛伊戰爭時期左右面（你當4000至5000年前），有個女祭師叫 卡珊德拉 ，佢拒絕咗阿波羅嘅強姦，阿波羅懲罰佢所講嘅預言全部唔會有人信，最後佢比阿伽門儂(討伐特洛伊嘅 &lsquo;大英雄&rsquo; ) 俘虜咗返希臘，繼而比阿伽門儂老婆殺死。<br />\n而老母話比我知，真相係卡珊德拉返緊希臘中途，阿波羅今次真係強姦咗佢。真係好撚仆街，不過就係咁，呢一個先知/ 詛咒嘅血統流撚到今日。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n卡珊德拉俾人殺死仲會有後代？<br />\n就算運送途中生咗，個仔唔會俾人清算埋一份？<br />\n<br />\n點解幾千年前啲神咁易向世俗現身，但依家2016年連影都唔見？"},{"pid":"6549625da6fd0186a7ef451f599e56be603718e5","tid":100702,"uid":20066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:34:42.000Z","msg":"你同正常人有咩分別"},{"pid":"1a087bb77ebfb049458cbbee85b562a0457c2cec","tid":100702,"uid":34836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:36:54.000Z","msg":"有一個農場，雞既數目是鴨既四倍，但係鴨又比豬少九隻。<br />\n鴨同豬既數目係六十七隻。請問農場所有動物既腳加埋有幾多隻？"},{"pid":"f835509c48c93cccb8a80d4edc80f7e8116aa447","tid":100702,"uid":10464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:42:22.000Z","msg":"巴打混血定外國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解開喺講故台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62b5bff54756a5669e518837c408bab9c77248b","tid":100702,"uid":19543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:43:03.000Z","msg":"點樣證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50abbeb1bf499044b7de24bf9a9f6538f2f9d3d8","tid":100702,"uid":418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:46:57.000Z","msg":"先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 預唔預到我幾時做你老豆"},{"pid":"35e6fb1cb2e51d9ac2cd551756c59f6de9bd7e41","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:47:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>是咁的，<br />\n細細個嘅時候老母已經講好多希臘神話比我聽，我仲奇怪緊點解佢咁撚熟嗰度嘅歷史。直到年初一佢話比我知，我係阿波羅先知嘅後人。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多巴絲都問我有無病，我具體少少講自己background 先。<br />\n<br />\n喺特洛伊戰爭時期左右面（你當4000至5000年前），有個女祭師叫 卡珊德拉 ，佢拒絕咗阿波羅嘅強姦，阿波羅懲罰佢所講嘅預言全部唔會有人信，最後佢比阿伽門儂(討伐特洛伊嘅 &lsquo;大英雄&rsquo; ) 俘虜咗返希臘，繼而比阿伽門儂老婆殺死。<br />\n而老母話比我知，真相係卡珊德拉返緊希臘中途，阿波羅今次真係強姦咗佢。真係好撚仆街，不過就係咁，呢一個先知/ 詛咒嘅血統流撚到今日。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n卡珊德拉俾人殺死仲會有後代？<br />\n就算運送途中生咗，個仔唔會俾人清算埋一份？<br />\n<br />\n點解幾千年前啲神咁易向世俗現身，但依家2016年連影都唔見？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. 天神生b 好快生，呢頭中出嗰頭生<br />\n2. 老豆係阿波羅，有寧芙照顧<br />\n3. 而家都大把人見過佛祖 你唔信姐， 仲有，我老母唔識上連登高登咪無人知"},{"pid":"286a4434d25b7f48dba526ca1a190ee35e7e2319","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:48:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打混血定外國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解開喺講故台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e31cc42b405f582ae892c09d9303335d4533fd","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:51:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不要問，只要信。<br />\n就算我偷把聖火出嚟，都唔會有人信架啦"},{"pid":"3a0cee41b35bcc087a8fb55cc399e52ba8312583","tid":100702,"uid":30934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T11:09:48.000Z","msg":"點睇車神 賭神 食神 女神 歌神同小丑神<br />\n呢班神同你個班熟唔熟？<br />\n呢班神交配生出黎既後代會唔會有特別既能力？<br />\n如果有 有無收留呢班後代既地方？<br />\n利申 讀神學 要寫論文 希望巴打可以詳細啲講"},{"pid":"e7a625a44b2ef38066f65b2be68f8042879e53e9","tid":100702,"uid":9091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T11:15:15.000Z","msg":"你係先知後人，我咪波賽東托世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾時叫我姪仔搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9c151482d72202ece7dc9bacfecaf92c74898e","tid":100702,"uid":7416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T11:21:28.000Z","msg":"咁你呀媽又係佢有佢地啲血統呀？<br />\n咁你即係半先知？你老豆應該都係正常人姐<br />\n咁你有冇咩技能呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dff756dec7301244835eaa68650ad8c1e9e999d","tid":100702,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T11:23:15.000Z","msg":"前幾日用左幾次銀河爆烈拳<br />\n係咪震傷左你個腦"},{"pid":"a13f85cd48bf015661d1f532d164ce4cfd512d6c","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:39:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇車神 賭神 食神 女神 歌神同小丑神<br />\n呢班神同你個班熟唔熟？<br />\n呢班神交配生出黎既後代會唔會有特別既能力？<br />\n如果有 有無收留呢班後代既地方？<br />\n利申 讀神學 要寫論文 希望巴打可以詳細啲講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1 第一題同神學有咩關系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2 我唔係神，神同神生出嚟嘅能力連父母都唔知，eg 毒撚火神、雅典娜 由宙斯個頭爆出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n3 你唔係想我答professor x 收留佢哋下話？"},{"pid":"d91651a646d331820badd4d6e6d49601ab8c26fb","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:40:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前幾日用左幾次銀河爆烈拳<br />\n係咪震傷左你個腦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能係"},{"pid":"ac30425e188728b64928053b923c71726c90b6b5","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你呀媽又係佢有佢地啲血統呀？<br />\n咁你即係半先知？你老豆應該都係正常人姐<br />\n咁你有冇咩技能呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無技能，<br />\n1 諸神去到 第四、五代，能力已經大不如前。<br />\n烏拉諾斯----克羅諾斯-----宙斯------荷米斯------潘。去到潘已經唔勁仲好古怪。<br />\n<br />\n過咗咁耐，咩能力都無"},{"pid":"4909fdee5a6a15ec3d9060225fba7766bc67662a","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:48:44.000Z","msg":"希臘啲神好撚小器，有個故仔係，阿波羅同阿提蜜斯(月亮女神，阿波羅家姐)個老母麗朵，有次咗嬲一個凡人，因為凡人自稱自己靚過麗朵，阿波羅同阿提蜜斯夾手夾腳射撚死佢全家。<br />\n我係驚多過信，因為不嬲都無咩神諭能力定咩，都係一條毒撚(屌你老味又話阿波羅好撚靚仔好叻音樂。又唔撚見我有) 。不過老母講，我我都當聽下就算。<br />\n等啲親戚走咗，佢話我哋所知嘅特洛伊戰爭/ 木馬屠城記打完之後，係有後續。唔知大家知唔知特洛伊戰爭誘發點係咩，以下我Copy返Wiki<br />\n<br />\n//婚宴上的金蘋果<br />\n在色薩利國王佩琉斯及海洋女神忒提斯的婚禮上，只有不和女神厄里斯沒被邀請參加，厄里斯心懷不憤，便想出詭計，將一個寫著「給最美麗的女神」的金蘋果扔在宴會上，送給赫拉、雅典娜及阿佛羅狄忒三個女神。三個女神各自理所當然的認為自己是金蘋果的應得者，爭持不下後唯有請求宙斯裁判，但宙斯卻拒絕作出裁判，於是三位女神就帶著蘋果到伊達山上，找特洛伊國王普里阿摩斯的兒子帕里斯作出裁決。[1]<br />\n帕里斯的裁決<br />\n帕里斯是普里阿摩斯及赫庫芭的兒子。赫庫芭生他前作了一個噩夢，夢到特洛伊受大火洗禮，預言家告訴赫庫芭這個兒子將毀了特洛伊，因此普里阿摩斯就把帕里斯拋棄在伊達山，後來由阿戈拉奧斯養大了他。<br />\n此時三個女神來到帕里斯的面前要他作裁決，三個女神都以獎品誘惑他，赫拉答應給他當全亞洲的王，雅典娜給他最高的軍功，而阿芙羅狄忒則給他世上最漂亮的女子海倫作妻，最後帕里斯把金蘋果交了給阿芙羅狄忒，成了阿芙羅狄忒的寵兒，而赫拉及雅典娜則因此決心毀滅特洛伊人。<br />\n其後，帕里斯在特洛伊競技會上力壓其他對手，並被普里阿摩斯認出而正式成為王子，帕里斯受到阿芙羅狄忒的唆使，乘船到斯巴達找海倫，他和朋友埃涅阿斯作為客人探訪斯巴達國王墨涅拉奧斯，宴上帕里斯及海倫互生情愫。過了幾天，趁著墨涅拉奧斯到克里特島時，帕里斯就唆使海倫離開丈夫，跟他同赴特洛伊，海倫為了愛情拋棄家庭，三天後他們就回到了特洛伊。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老母話愛神收咗呢粒金蘋果，打完曬特洛伊之後，赫拉(宙斯老婆) 都仲係好想佔有呢粒金蘋果，屌你我心諗而家成街都係Apple 啦，落冥界搵Steve Jobs 啦仆街！赫拉唔想愛神永遠都係最靚嘅女神，覺得整爛咗Iphone 就有得再選過。所以佢派左兩條蛇去咬粒蘋果，結果係成功得逞，愛神同戰神(又) 偷情期間，粒金蘋果霉撚咗。赫拉向宙斯要求重新選過大美人，不過特洛伊戰爭打完之後，宙斯覺得好撚大陣仗，勞民傷財，叫呢三個女神自己私下解決。老母講到呢度就話佢啲神諭去到呢度，剩返嘅內容要我等我收喎⋯⋯屌你老味，卡珊德拉女祭司當但比阿波羅因姦成孕，點知阿波羅會唔會執我番皂Sosad，阿波羅有有Gay前科架！"},{"pid":"14a79b829cd64946dc75cad4007638a6bdc880b1","tid":100702,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:25:49.000Z","msg":"巴打今年讀中二?"},{"pid":"75e18b544a76a292ef2169ced7141c1d3e64db83","tid":100702,"uid":606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:18:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打今年讀中二?</blockquote><br />\n應該係"},{"pid":"c7214c8373a25df297f092531e9cf956bff9ff7c","tid":100702,"uid":74353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:54:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打今年讀中二?</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"7af56fa2b4f6ee44e41a98f17c48e8ac441fdbe6","tid":100702,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:41:25.000Z","msg":"無技能咁先乜野知"},{"pid":"b45fa1d02a7a21329f142ef0604e3d1d30945567","tid":100702,"uid":73935,"like":0,"di